<H1>Changing the PAGER environment variable</H1>

<P>Other commands such as <STRONG>man</STRONG> and <STRONG>mail</STRONG>
use a pager to
display their output on the screen.  The default pager
used by these commands is defined by the PAGER
environment variable.</P>

<P>You can change the default pager by <A HREF="../environment/index.html">setting or
changing</A> the value of this variable.</P>

